<h3>New Post</h3>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Guidelines for posts</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Make sure it rhymes.</li>
      <li>Don't use the letter "A".</li>
      <li>The incessant use of hashtags will get you banned.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <%= render partial: 'form', locals: { category: @category, post: @post, call_back: category_path(@category) } %>
  </div>
</div>